snippet.title: Kick Off 96 gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Kick Off 96, Dos PC game produced by Anco Software in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/kick-off-96/8462/
Playing in cup mode with Italy. Loosing first match against Germany (France winning final).
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
